I'll call you later. Okay? Bye.

1084
01:50:05.156 --> 01:50:06.173 line:82%
Who was that?

1085
01:50:06.267 --> 01:50:09.136 line:82%
That was Priya.
She keeps calling and boring me.

1086
01:50:09.562 --> 01:50:13.387 line:82%
Now you go change your clothes,
and I will make you some hot coffee.

1087
01:50:14.442 --> 01:50:17.403 line:82%
-Hey. Who's that Priya bothering you?
-Let it go, Papa.

1088
01:50:39.175 --> 01:50:44.540 line:82%
Papa, I have come to apologize to you.

1089
01:50:45.723 --> 01:50:47.367 line:82%
Apologize? For what?

1090
01:50:52.146 --> 01:50:57.568 line:82%
Papa, you always taught me never to lie,

1091
01:50:59.236 --> 01:51:01.030 line:82%
but I lied to you.

1092
01:51:02.865 --> 01:51:07.078 line:82%
That day, when you were in my room
and the phone rang,

1093
01:51:08.245 --> 01:51:13.135 line:82%
I told you it was Priya
but it was not Priya, Papa.

1094
01:51:15.294 --> 01:51:16.310 line:82%
It was someone else.

1095
01:51:17.296 --> 01:51:18.332 line:82%
Who was it?

1096
01:51:21.092 --> 01:51:22.385 line:82%
It was a boy.

1097
01:51:26.972 --> 01:51:29.801 line:82%
A boy whom I have known
for a very long time,

1098
01:51:31.852 --> 01:51:35.775 line:82%
someone who has come to be
more than a friend to me.

1099
01:51:38.776 --> 01:51:42.279 line:82%
A boy who loves me very much.

1100
01:51:44.740 --> 01:51:46.894 line:82%
Someone I also love very much.

1101
01:51:51.015 --> 01:51:55.110 line:82%
I know I should have told you earlier.

1102
01:51:56.919 --> 01:51:59.260 line:82%
But I was scared that you would get angry.

1103
01:52:00.798 --> 01:52:06.720 line:82%
You have always told me
that love leads to pain.

1104
01:52:09.765 --> 01:52:12.601 line:82%
But I do not know what it is about him,

1105
01:52:13.769 --> 01:52:16.555 line:82%
but I just could not stop myself
from walking this path.

1106
01:52:18.607 --> 01:52:24.326 line:82%
When you meet him,
you will realize that how different he is,

1107
01:52:25.531 --> 01:52:29.151 line:82%
how sweet he is, how true he is.

1108
01:52:31.454 --> 01:52:36.375 line:82%
You had prayed
that all my wishes come true,

1109
01:52:37.209 --> 01:52:38.513 line:82%
all my dreams come true.

1110
01:52:41.382 --> 01:52:46.762 line:82%
He is my one and only dream.

1111
01:52:48.637 --> 01:52:51.826 line:82%
-I do not want anything else. I--
-What's his name?

1112
01:52:56.020 --> 01:52:59.460 line:82%
Raj. Raj Malhotra.

1113
01:53:00.608 --> 01:53:01.817 line:82%
What does he do?

1114
01:53:03.903 --> 01:53:07.254 line:82%
He's a student in Gurukul.

1115
01:53:13.120 --> 01:53:14.610 line:82%
You are not angry, Papa, are you?

1116
01:53:17.041 --> 01:53:18.460 line:82%
Papa, please don't be angry.

1117
01:53:22.880 --> 01:53:26.301 line:82%
I... I love him, Papa, I love him.

1118
01:53:28.482 --> 01:53:29.757 line:82%
I love him, Papa.

1119
01:53:31.058 --> 01:53:32.232 line:82%
I love him.

1120
01:53:59.416 --> 01:54:00.668 line:82%
I am here to inform you

1121
01:54:00.751 --> 01:54:02.896 line:82%
that Raj Malhotra has been expelled
from Gurukul.

1122
01:54:05.089 --> 01:54:09.260 line:82%
I did not meet him,
I do not know what he looks like,

1123
01:54:09.343 --> 01:54:11.291 line:82%
and I hope I never see him.

1124
01:54:14.640 --> 01:54:16.976 line:82%
I have sent him somewhere
far away from here,

1125
01:54:17.059 --> 01:54:18.700 line:82%
and I would like you to forget him.

1126
01:54:21.313 --> 01:54:24.239 line:82%
I know you must be thinking

1127
01:54:26.193 --> 01:54:29.613 line:82%
that my decision is cruel and wrong,

1128
01:54:29.697 --> 01:54:35.077 line:82%
but I know that this is the best thing

1129
01:54:35.828 --> 01:54:37.442 line:82%
for your future.

1130
01:55:17.828 --> 01:55:19.163 line:82%
Good morning, Papa.

1131
01:55:32.051 --> 01:55:36.138 line:82%
Your tea is over there,
but the newspaper guy has still not come.

1132
01:55:36.587 --> 01:55:39.212 line:82%
It's Sunday,
so I think he is running a little late.

1133
01:55:40.059 --> 01:55:42.603 line:82%
By the way, Bahadur is unwell.

1134
01:55:43.020 --> 01:55:46.062 line:82%
So let me know what you will have
for breakfast, I will make it myself.

1135
01:55:55.699 --> 01:55:56.867 line:82%
Are you all right?

1136
01:55:58.786 --> 01:56:01.954 line:82%
I am absolutely fine, Papa
I am absolutely fine.

1137
01:56:07.419 --> 01:56:10.797 line:82%
Thats enough, it's quite late.

1138
01:56:11.173 --> 01:56:13.989 line:82%
And you have to get up early
in the morning. Open your mouth.

1139
01:56:27.272 --> 01:56:30.492 line:82%
Do you know that
you are the world's best daughter?

1140
01:56:34.321 --> 01:56:35.406 line:82%
Are you happy?

1141
01:56:36.532 --> 01:56:39.172 line:82%
-Are you happy, Papa?
-Very much.

1142
01:56:40.285 --> 01:56:44.566 line:82%
Then I am also very happy.
Good night, Papa.

1143
01:57:21.688 --> 01:57:25.664 line:82%
I'm sorry, Papa.
I tried really hard to forget him.

1144
01:57:26.814 --> 01:57:29.227 line:82%
I tried very hard not to think about him,

1145
01:57:30.252 --> 01:57:34.656 line:82%
to stop loving him...but I just could not.

1146
01:57:36.300 --> 01:57:38.552 line:82%
I love you very much, Papa.

1147
01:57:39.344 --> 01:57:44.499 line:82%
And I can never see you upset,
but I love him, too,

1148
01:57:45.494 --> 01:57:47.274 line:82%
and I cannot live without him.

1149
01:57:50.663 --> 01:57:55.302 line:82%
I hope, someday,
you realize that love is very beautiful,

1150
01:57:56.653 --> 01:58:00.407 line:82%
even if it comes with a little pain.

1151
01:58:03.866 --> 01:58:05.200 line:82%
I am sorry, Papa.

1152
01:58:07.331 --> 01:58:08.332 line:82%
I am sorry.

1153
01:58:11.640 --> 01:58:15.005 line:82%
Megha!

1154
01:59:21.280 --> 01:59:26.451 line:82%
Ever since the day she told me
about you, I have hated you.

1155
01:59:28.537 --> 01:59:33.000 line:82%
I hated you so much
that I never wanted to see your face.

1156
01:59:34.376 --> 01:59:36.086 line:82%
I never ever wanted to hear your voice,

1157
01:59:38.255 --> 01:59:40.941 line:82%
and today you are standing
in front of me on my doorstep.

1158
01:59:43.510 --> 01:59:47.055 line:82%
If I wished, I could drag you
out of that gate, and throw you out

1159
01:59:47.571 --> 01:59:52.936 line:82%
and no piece of paper can stop me,
but I am not going to do that.

1160
01:59:54.980 --> 01:59:56.563 line:82%
Because now I want you to stay.

1161
01:59:59.234 --> 02:00:03.864 line:82%
You have given a 55-year-old, tired man

1162
02:00:05.032 --> 02:00:07.075 line:82%
a reason to fight again,

1163
02:00:10.120 --> 02:00:15.876 line:82%
He has to prove all over again that,
for 25 years whatever,

1164
02:00:15.959 --> 02:00:18.579 line:82%
he has stood for and believed in,
still holds true.

1165
02:00:22.466 --> 02:00:24.020 line:82%
You were right about me, Mr. Aryan.

1166
02:00:26.929 --> 02:00:30.432 line:82%
Like you, even I love challenges.

1167
02:00:32.893 --> 02:00:34.556 line:82%
So, now you do what you have to,

1168
02:00:36.438 --> 02:00:39.066 line:82%
and I'll do what I have been doing
for the last 25 years.

1169
02:00:41.693 --> 02:00:43.487 line:82%
The foundation of this structure

1170
02:00:44.363 --> 02:00:48.533 line:82%
is so strong that no Raj Aryan,

1171
02:00:48.617 --> 02:00:52.484 line:82%
with a violin in his hand
and a smile on his face,

1172
02:00:53.455 --> 02:00:56.184 line:82%
will ever dare to walk in here
to change things around.

1173
02:00:58.547 --> 02:00:59.715 line:82%
Never, Mr. Raj Aryan.

1174
02:01:02.255 --> 02:01:03.674 line:82%
Never.

1175
02:01:15.143 --> 02:01:18.814 line:82%
Megha, you were right.

1176
02:01:20.190 --> 02:01:22.487 line:82%
It's not easy to win from your father.

1177
02:01:23.706 --> 02:01:30.589 line:82%
He is one tough man, but we are no less.

1178
02:01:52.921 --> 02:01:57.398 line:82%
Hey, Vicky! Vicky, give it back.
Sameer, I am warning you.

1179
02:02:01.658 --> 02:02:02.691 line:82%
Oh, shit!

1180
02:02:02.774 --> 02:02:04.433 line:82%
-Good morning, sir.
-Good morning.

1181
02:02:04.528 --> 02:02:06.194 line:82%
Do any of you know how to play the piano?

1182
02:02:06.987 --> 02:02:10.657 line:82%
It's okay.
I needed somebody to teach

1183
02:02:10.741 --> 02:02:15.162 line:82%
Major Khanna's grandson, but never mind,
maybe someone else would know.

1184
02:02:15.620 --> 02:02:16.732 line:82%
Cool room.

1185
02:02:19.499 --> 02:02:20.913 line:82%
-Vicky, man.
-Hey, Vicky,

1186
02:02:22.220 --> 02:02:25.391 line:82%
haven't we heard
this name before, Major Khanna.

1187
02:02:26.506 --> 02:02:27.507 line:82%
Oh, shit.

1188
02:02:29.509 --> 02:02:30.527 line:82%
Oh, shit.

1189
02:02:36.975 --> 02:02:39.401 line:82%
So, you would like to learn the piano,
right?

1190
02:02:40.062 --> 02:02:41.081 line:82%
Yes, sir.

1191
02:02:42.773 --> 02:02:43.857 line:82%
Major Khanna.

1192
02:02:44.564 --> 02:02:46.908 line:82%
Come down in 10 minutes,
we have a lot of work to do.

1193
02:02:47.477 --> 02:02:50.489 line:82%
-Yes, sir.
-And do come with some clothes on.

1194
02:03:15.639 --> 02:03:17.808 line:82%
-Well done, Karan.
-Thank you, sir.

1195
02:03:18.225 --> 02:03:22.854 line:82%
Now, Ayush, I want you
to learn to play the piano

1196
02:03:23.605 --> 02:03:25.107 line:82%
before your father comes back.

1197
02:03:25.190 --> 02:03:28.819 line:82%
Do not worry, sir, in one month
he will be playing even better than me.

1198
02:03:29.071 --> 02:03:30.779 line:82%
-Right, Ayush?
-Right.

1199
02:03:31.012 --> 02:03:33.183 line:82%
-Okay, Karan, I am leaving, you carry on.
-Yes, sir.

1200
02:03:33.646 --> 02:03:34.699 line:82%
Right, Ayush?

1201
02:03:34.786 --> 02:03:36.243 line:82%
-Right.
-Good.

1202
02:03:37.804 --> 02:03:39.351 line:82%
Come on, let's start.

1203
02:03:39.438 --> 02:03:44.470 line:82%
Karan, just a minute, this is
our younger daughter-in-law Kiran,

1204
02:03:44.918 --> 02:03:47.552 line:82%
and this is Karan Choudhary,
Ayush's piano teacher.

1205
02:03:48.338 --> 02:03:49.920 line:82%
Hi, nice to meet you.

1206
02:03:50.579 --> 02:03:52.845 line:82%
-Namaste.
-Namaste.

1207
02:03:53.927 --> 02:03:56.096 line:82%
Karan, if you do not mind,

1208
02:03:56.337 --> 02:03:59.266 line:82%
-can you teach her too, along with Ayush?
-Bhabhi!

1209
02:03:59.349 --> 02:04:03.603 line:82%
Hold on, she loves music,
in fact she has learned classical dance.

1210
02:04:03.687 --> 02:04:05.053 line:82%
-Bhabhi.
-Okay.

1211
02:04:05.586 --> 02:04:07.190 line:82%
Okay, she does not do it anymore.

1212
02:04:07.315 --> 02:04:12.362 line:82%
Thank God she doesn't, otherwise
she used to disturb me every morning.

1213
02:04:12.445 --> 02:04:14.197 line:82%
-Ayush, stop it.
-You stop it.

1214
02:04:18.076 --> 02:04:19.121 line:82%
All the best.

1215
02:04:20.120 --> 02:04:23.540 line:82%
Okay. Time out.
Ayush, get me a glass of water.

1216
02:04:23.832 --> 02:04:24.886 line:82%
Sister, get water.

1217
02:04:25.584 --> 02:04:29.295 line:82%
Ayush, this is wrong, your sister is elder
than you, you go and get me water.

1218
02:04:29.838 --> 02:04:31.840 line:82%
Okay. In this house
I have to do all the work.

1219
02:04:31.923 --> 02:04:32.924 line:82%
Shut up.

1220
02:04:33.842 --> 02:04:35.427 line:82%
Ramu kaka, water!

1221
02:04:36.887 --> 02:04:39.332 line:82%
You never told me that you used to dance?

1222
02:04:39.973 --> 02:04:46.188 line:82%
What is there to say in that?
Anyway, I used to dance, I do not anymore.

1223
02:04:46.938 --> 02:04:48.028 line:82%
Why?

1224
02:04:48.648 --> 02:04:52.101 line:82%
-You ask too many questions.
-That's because you never answer.

1225
02:04:53.111 --> 02:04:56.035 line:82%
Have you come here to teach Ayush
piano lessons or to chat with me?

1226
02:04:58.241 --> 02:04:59.284 line:82%
What do you think?

1227
02:05:11.421 --> 02:05:16.887 line:82%
Ishika, my child, meet your new dance
partner Vikram, not Viren, right?

1228
02:05:17.177 --> 02:05:18.178 line:82%
Right.

1229
02:05:18.678 --> 02:05:22.098 line:82%
Okay, Vikram, I want you know
that this dance competition

1230
02:05:22.174 --> 02:05:24.925 line:82%
is a matter of prestige for our college,

1231
02:05:25.602 --> 02:05:31.035 line:82%
and that is why, on my request,
Mr. Raj Aryan has sent you to help us out.

1232
02:05:31.441 --> 02:05:33.946 line:82%
What a wonderful man he is. God bless him.

1233
02:05:34.611 --> 02:05:38.371 line:82%
Ishika, I want you both
to befriend each other

1234
02:05:38.907 --> 02:05:42.318 line:82%
and in a month's time,
show me something really special.

1235
02:05:42.911 --> 02:05:44.037 line:82%
-Okay?
-Yes, ma'am.

1236
02:05:44.120 --> 02:05:46.957 line:82%
-But no fighting. Okay?
- -Yes, ma'am.

1237
02:05:50.795 --> 02:05:54.632 line:82%
Don't make your already stupid face
look even more stupid.

1238
02:05:55.674 --> 02:06:00.350 line:82%
In case you don't know, I've won this
dance competition for three years running,

1239
02:06:01.179 --> 02:06:05.091 line:82%
and I am not going to end up losing
this year because of an idiot like you.

1240
02:06:06.017 --> 02:06:10.438 line:82%
So if you do not wish to make
a fool of yourself, just leave quietly.

1241
02:06:10.522 --> 02:06:14.567 line:82%
No, please, don't do that.
I have been waiting for this all my life.

1242
02:06:14.818 --> 02:06:19.216 line:82%
All I have ever wanted is to be able
to dance with you. That's it.

1243
02:06:19.572 --> 02:06:25.078 line:82%
After this, even if I die I will have
no regrets. Please dance with me.

1244
02:06:25.726 --> 02:06:27.281 line:82%
Please!

1245
02:06:27.902 --> 02:06:32.666 line:82%
Your sense of humor is just like you,
sick and disgusting.

1246
02:06:33.187 --> 02:06:34.204 line:82%
Hey, Ishq.

1247
02:06:34.379 --> 02:06:39.050 line:82%
-My name is lshika!
-My friends feel that I was rude

1248
02:06:39.301 --> 02:06:42.804 line:82%
to you the other day,
when you had come to apologize.

1249
02:06:43.573 --> 02:06:49.019 line:82%
-And what do you feel?
-I think they are right. I am sorry.

1250
02:06:50.145 --> 02:06:51.988 line:82%
-It's okay.
-Friends?

1251
02:06:53.189 --> 02:06:54.649 line:82%
-Friends.
-Cool.

1252
02:06:54.983 --> 02:06:56.318 line:82%
Now, can you let me go?

1253
02:06:57.385 --> 02:06:58.674 line:82%
I don't feel like it.

1254
02:06:59.529 --> 02:07:01.990 line:82%
Oh? Do you feel like getting a slap?

1255
02:07:03.658 --> 02:07:04.701 line:82%
Sure.

1256
02:07:06.473 --> 02:07:08.204 line:82%
-If the girl smiles, she's yours.
-What?

1257
02:07:08.830 --> 02:07:09.831 line:82%
Nothing.

1258
02:07:10.415 --> 02:07:13.321 line:82%
-Okay, let me go.
-Let you go?

1259
02:07:13.918 --> 02:07:14.961 line:82%
Please.

1260
02:07:16.421 --> 02:07:17.547 line:82%
Okay.

1261
02:07:17.988 --> 02:07:19.024 line:82%
Stupid.

1262
02:07:20.175 --> 02:07:21.176 line:82%
I love her.

1263
02:07:57.128 --> 02:07:59.433 line:82%
-Mr. Aryan, you didn't join us?
-I am just...

1264
02:08:01.925 --> 02:08:03.343 line:82%
-Hi, how are you?
-Morning, sir.

1265
02:08:03.426 --> 02:08:05.178 line:82%
Come, come,
I need to talk to you guys.

1266
02:08:05.261 --> 02:08:06.304 line:82%
Mr. Raj Aryan.

1267
02:08:09.224 --> 02:08:10.595 line:82%
-You guys carry on.
-Yes, sir.

1268
02:08:16.898 --> 02:08:19.585 line:82%
I would like to remind you
that till you are a part of Gurukul,

1269
02:08:19.658 --> 02:08:23.029 line:82%
it is your duty to follow
the traditions of this place.

1270
02:08:23.988 --> 02:08:27.634 line:82%
Next time, I do not want to see you
outside the temple.

1271
02:08:28.451 --> 02:08:31.700 line:82%
I'm sorry, sir,
but I will not come into the temple.

1272
02:08:34.124 --> 02:08:36.061 line:82%
I have an old score to settle with him,

1273
02:08:36.835 --> 02:08:40.839 line:82%
he took the one person
who believed in him the most.

1274
02:08:42.465 --> 02:08:44.509 line:82%
Challenging us mortals
was not enough for you,

1275
02:08:44.592 --> 02:08:46.153 line:82%
that you have decided to take on God.

1276
02:08:46.594 --> 02:08:49.872 line:82%
No, sir, my God is within me.

1277
02:08:52.725 --> 02:08:54.294 line:82%
I do not believe in any other God.

1278
02:08:57.397 --> 02:08:58.857 line:82%
Mr. Raj Aryan...

1279
02:09:03.528 --> 02:09:07.449 line:82%
Take this, prasad, for all your battles.

1280
02:09:08.575 --> 02:09:11.536 line:82%
I'm sorry, sir,
but I cannot take even this.

1281
02:09:12.704 --> 02:09:16.916 line:82%
Because to take this, I would have
to touch your feet, like the others.

1282
02:09:18.126 --> 02:09:20.628 line:82%
And that is something
that my heart will not allow me to do.

1283
02:09:20.712 --> 02:09:23.339 line:82%
I do not force anyone to touch my feet,
Mr. Aryan.

1284
02:09:24.424 --> 02:09:27.677 line:82%
They do it out of respect.

1285
02:09:28.720 --> 02:09:33.224 line:82%
They touch your feet out of fear
and you mistake their fear for respect.

1286
02:09:34.135 --> 02:09:35.179 line:82%
But I'm...

1287
02:09:35.280 --> 02:09:38.813 line:82%
But you are not scared of me, Mr. Aryan.
I know that...

1288
02:09:41.232 --> 02:09:43.483 line:82%
The other day you had put the tilaka
on my forehead,

1289
02:09:44.694 --> 02:09:47.405 line:82%
but I had nothing to give you.

1290
02:09:49.199 --> 02:09:51.913 line:82%
Today, accept this as a blessing
for that day,

1291
02:09:53.578 --> 02:09:55.218 line:82%
it would relieve a burden from my head,

1292
02:09:56.456 --> 02:09:59.054 line:82%
and make us even.

1293
02:10:00.502 --> 02:10:01.521 line:82%
And yes,

1294
